info:

The setting is the Riviera in autumn. A retired English businessman
has just been through heart surgery but it has, apparently, done
little to relieve his constant pain or improve his long-term
survival prospects. During his recuperation Caroline, his adult
daughter, comes from Paris to be with him and her mother, Miche,
and she and her father begin to communicate as adults for the first time.
